cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.SI, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a metric learning algorithm that specifically considers relational data, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and databases (cs.DB). The paper also introduces a link-strength function that measures the strength of relationship links between entities, which is related to the field of social network analysis (cs.SI) and natural language processing (cs.CL) where relationships between entities are also important.
